[Oh Min Seong: I heard a phone ring
on the first floor.]

424
00:27:52,400 --> 00:27:55,200
[Taichi: Hmm?]
[Oh Min Seong: A phone downstairs rang.]

425
00:27:55,210 --> 00:27:56,990
[Taichi: You don't know who he is.]

426
00:27:56,990 --> 00:27:59,220
[Oh Min Seong: I've got it.]

427
00:27:59,230 --> 00:28:00,880
[Taichi: Did you get a call?]
[Oh Min Seong: Me?]

428
00:28:00,890 --> 00:28:04,060
[Taichi: Yeah.]
[Oh Min Seong: No, I didn't.]

429
00:28:04,070 --> 00:28:06,250
[Oh Min Seong: I said I didn't get a call.]

430
00:28:06,260 --> 00:28:09,890
[Taichi: Wait a little longer.
It's not over until it's over.]

431
00:28:10,040 --> 00:28:14,250
[Oh Min Seong: I said I didn't get a call.]
[Taichi: I heard you!]

432
00:28:14,780 --> 00:28:17,090
[Oh Min Seong: Why do you sound so fed up?]

433
00:28:17,090 --> 00:28:20,170
[Taichi: There's still a chance,
so don't give up.]

434
00:28:20,770 --> 00:28:23,040
[Oh Min Seong: I didn't get a call.]

435
00:28:23,050 --> 00:28:25,650
[Oh Min Seong: I thought I'd get his call.]

436
00:28:25,670 --> 00:28:28,570
[Oh Min Seong: Or I'd storm to his room.]

437
00:28:30,150 --> 00:28:32,890
[Oh Min Seong:
But it was a really long wait.]

438
00:28:32,910 --> 00:28:37,830
[Oh Min Seong: "What if..."
I got a bit worried.]

439
00:28:38,500 --> 00:28:40,780
He looks sturdy and good in this photo.

440
00:28:39,820 --> 00:28:41,620
[Staring]

441
00:28:41,930 --> 00:28:45,840
[Hyeong Jun is just staring at his phone]

442
00:28:43,460 --> 00:28:45,800
To be exact, it's when he grabbed his knees.

443
00:28:45,800 --> 00:28:47,300
Oh, yeah?

444
00:28:45,940 --> 00:28:48,610
[He finally gets the text]

445
00:28:50,140 --> 00:28:52,270
[Lee Hyeong Jun,
please head to the Phone Room.]

446
00:28:52,270 --> 00:28:55,210
[Within 30 seconds, convey your feelings
to the man you are drawn to today.]

447
00:29:01,920 --> 00:29:06,720
[A day with Min Seong
that washed away his pain]

448
00:29:15,270 --> 00:29:20,200
[Will Hyeong Jun
convey his feelings to Min Seong?]

449
00:29:26,700 --> 00:29:28,900
[Taichi: See? I told you.]

450
00:29:28,900 --> 00:29:30,580
[Oh Min Seong: Hello?]

451
00:29:30,580 --> 00:29:32,660
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Hello.]

452
00:29:32,680 --> 00:29:34,310
[Oh Min Seong: Who are you?]

453
00:29:39,910 --> 00:29:41,980
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Hmm...]

454
00:29:42,210 --> 00:29:43,810
[Oh Min Seong: 30 seconds is short.]

455
00:29:46,040 --> 00:29:49,120
[Lee Hyeong Jun: You're the only one
I could call, so I called you.]

456
00:29:49,130 --> 00:29:51,030
[Oh Min Seong: What was that?]

457
00:29:52,940 --> 00:29:55,740
[Oh Min Seong: You sound so uncool.]

458
00:29:55,740 --> 00:29:57,450
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Wait, I think
I called the wrong person.]

459
00:29:57,450 --> 00:29:59,570
[Oh Min Seong: What?]

460
00:30:02,940 --> 00:30:05,100
[Oh Min Seong:
Please convey your feelings.]

461
00:30:06,590 --> 00:30:07,960
[Oh Min Seong: It was cut off.]

462
00:30:07,970 --> 00:30:10,850
[Taichi: I told you you'd get a call.]

463
00:30:10,850 --> 00:30:13,180
[Oh Min Seong: 30 seconds is too short.]

464
00:30:13,190 --> 00:30:16,710
[Oh Min Seong: I had mixed feelings.]

465
00:30:16,710 --> 00:30:19,600
[Oh Min Seong: "You were the only one
I could call" can mean]

466
00:30:19,630 --> 00:30:23,500
[Oh Min Seong: he had no other options,
or that he only has feelings for me.]

467
00:30:23,500 --> 00:30:26,390
[Oh Min Seong: Why's he being like that?]

468
00:30:29,240 --> 00:30:32,850
[Lee Hyeong Jun: If I don't joke around,
he'll go even further with the jokes.]

469
00:30:32,860 --> 00:30:34,870
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
So I beat him to the punch.]

470
00:30:34,870 --> 00:30:37,480
[Lee Hyeong Jun: He must be
really comfortable with me now,]

471
00:30:37,480 --> 00:30:41,830
[Lee Hyeong Jun: because he was
not serious at all during the call.]

472
00:30:41,850 --> 00:30:44,050
[Lee Hyeong Jun: It made me speechless.]

473
00:30:44,050 --> 00:30:48,790
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I thought,
"What should I do with him?"]

474
00:30:51,500 --> 00:30:53,780
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Sigh, I'm really tired.]

475
00:30:53,800 --> 00:30:56,420
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
I'm sleepy, and my back hurts.]

476
00:31:03,220 --> 00:31:06,130
[Sun Wook looks exhausted too]

477
00:31:06,140 --> 00:31:09,160
[Kim Sun Wook: I was slowly getting angry.]

478
00:31:09,160 --> 00:31:12,730
[Kim Sun Wook:
More than anger, I got anxious.]

479
00:31:12,740 --> 00:31:15,480
[Kim Sun Wook:
Even if he's interested in me,]

480
00:31:15,480 --> 00:31:18,950
[Kim Sun Wook:
feelings can change anytime.]

481
00:31:18,950 --> 00:31:21,160
[Kim Sun Wook: It's not weird
for feelings to change at this time too.]

482
00:31:21,160 --> 00:31:28,130
[Kim Sun Wook: I started worrying
and having doubts.]

483
00:31:31,360 --> 00:31:32,990
[Lee Hyun Jun,
please head to the Phone Room.]

484
00:31:32,990 --> 00:31:34,820
[Within 30 seconds, convey your feelings
to the man you are drawn to today.]

485
00:31:44,060 --> 00:31:46,690
[Kim Han Gyeol: Has Hyun Jun called yet?]

486
00:31:46,720 --> 00:31:49,440
[Kim Han Gyeol:
You should pray for this now.]

487
00:31:49,450 --> 00:31:51,310
[Cho Yun Jae: I'm sure he won't call me.]

488
00:31:51,320 --> 00:31:53,650
[Cho Yun Jae: We talked today.]

489
00:31:53,650 --> 00:31:58,870
[Cho Yun Jae: He said he's 70%
leaning toward Sun Wook.]

490
00:31:58,890 --> 00:32:03,120
[Cho Yun Jae:
So he'll call Sun Wook today.]

491
00:32:03,120 --> 00:32:06,680
[Kim Han Gyeol:
But he might call you too. 30%.]

492
00:32:06,680 --> 00:32:09,140
[Cho Yun Jae:
But I don't want to have false hope.]

493
00:32:09,140 --> 00:32:12,020
[Cho Yun Jae:
I'd just end up getting hurt.]

494
00:32:12,020 --> 00:32:15,130
[Cho Yun Jae: I feel better
thinking he won't call me.]

495
00:32:15,140 --> 00:32:17,830
[Cho Yun Jae:
But I'll try to change his mind today.]

496
00:32:17,840 --> 00:32:23,620
[Cho Yun Jae: I asked him out
on a walk tonight, if there's time.]

497
00:32:24,170 --> 00:32:28,480
[His heavy steps
mirror his heavy heart]

498
00:32:45,560 --> 00:32:50,400
[Who will Hyun Jun convey his feelings to?]

499
00:32:53,670 --> 00:33:00,740
[Between Sun Wook and Yun Jae,
who will Hyun Jun choose?]

500
00:33:04,230 --> 00:33:06,880
[Hello?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Hello?]

501
00:33:06,880 --> 00:33:08,780
[Yes.]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Yes?]

502
00:33:09,220 --> 00:33:12,220
[Sun Wook gets shy
after getting Hyun Jun's call]

503
00:33:12,230 --> 00:33:16,900
[Lee Hyun Jun: It'd have been better
if we got to hang out alone today.]

504
00:33:16,900 --> 00:33:18,570
[Lee Hyun Jun: But it was still fun.]

505
00:33:18,570 --> 00:33:21,540
[Kim Sun Wook: Yeah.
We can hang out together next time.]

506
00:33:21,720 --> 00:33:23,660
[Lee Hyun Jun: I enjoyed the food too.
Thank you.]

507
00:33:24,130 --> 00:33:26,830
[Kim Sun Wook: OK. See you later.]

508
00:33:26,840 --> 00:33:29,100
[Lee Hyun Jun: See you later.]

509
00:33:31,860 --> 00:33:32,700
OK.

510
00:33:32,640 --> 00:33:37,410
[Sun Wook regains his smile]

511
00:33:44,940 --> 00:33:47,470
[Kim Sun Wook:
He's not the type to say all that.]

512
00:33:47,470 --> 00:33:50,890
[Kim Sun Wook:
So he must've given it much thought.]

513
00:33:50,890 --> 00:33:52,330
[Kim Sun Wook: That was
very thoughtful of him.]

514
00:33:52,340 --> 00:33:56,510
[Kim Sun Wook: I know he means no harm,
but he habitually gives very short responses.]

515
00:33:56,510 --> 00:34:00,110
[Kim Sun Wook: Having to
initiate the convo in the call,]

516
00:34:00,120 --> 00:34:03,490
[Kim Sun Wook: it must've taken him
much thought and courage.]

517
00:34:03,490 --> 00:34:05,160
[Kim Sun Wook: I thought
it was very thoughtful.]

518
00:34:05,160 --> 00:34:07,660
[Kim Sun Wook: And I was very happy.]

519
00:34:14,670 --> 00:34:18,500
[Lee Hyun Jun: He's the person
I like the most right now.]

520
00:34:18,500 --> 00:34:21,679
[Lee Hyun Jun: So I called him.]

521
00:34:28,560 --> 00:34:32,000
[The call time is over]

522
00:34:32,330 --> 00:34:37,139
[Taichi didn't get a single call]

523
00:34:37,909 --> 00:34:40,210
[And another person...]

524
00:34:42,040 --> 00:34:46,780
[Su Min, who's been waiting endlessly
for his call]

525
00:34:46,850 --> 00:34:49,449
[Kim Su Min: I didn't get his call.]

526
00:34:49,679 --> 00:34:52,870
[Kim Su Min: I didn't expect much,]

527
00:34:52,870 --> 00:34:55,730
[Kim Su Min: but I can't help feeling sad.]

528
00:34:56,739 --> 00:34:57,980
[Cho Yun Jae: Taichi.]
[Taichi: Hmm?]

529
00:34:57,990 --> 00:35:00,160
[Cho Yun Jae: Come here.]

530
00:35:08,900 --> 00:35:12,000
[Cho Yun Jae: I have something to ask you.]

531
00:35:11,500 --> 00:35:12,100
What is it?

532
00:35:12,010 --> 00:35:17,460
[Cho Yun Jae: You chose me on the first day.
Then you never chose me again.]

533
00:35:17,460 --> 00:35:21,400
[Cho Yun Jae: What's the reason?]

534
00:35:21,420 --> 00:35:25,700
[Taichi: I tend to get interested in people]

535
00:35:25,720 --> 00:35:29,130
[Taichi: who I feel relaxed with
and have fun with, regardless of looks.]

536
00:35:29,130 --> 00:35:30,910
[Taichi: On the first day, to be honest,]

537
00:35:30,920 --> 00:35:32,710
[Taichi: we were both nervous,]

538
00:35:32,740 --> 00:35:35,260
[Taichi: and I didn't see you feel relaxed.]

539
00:35:35,260 --> 00:35:39,070
[Taichi: So I felt uneasy too.]

540
00:35:39,080 --> 00:35:41,780
[Taichi: Compared to the first day,]

541
00:35:41,780 --> 00:35:44,480
[Taichi: it's much more fun
to talk to you.]

542
00:35:44,480 --> 00:35:47,050
[Taichi: Should I say
we share the same sense of humor?]

543
00:35:47,050 --> 00:35:48,250
[Taichi: So I've been a bit...]

544
00:35:48,250 --> 00:35:49,750
[Taichi: Like I said on the phone,]

545
00:35:49,760 --> 00:35:52,730
[Taichi: I'm still not sure
if it's romantic.]

546
00:35:52,820 --> 00:35:55,150
[Taichi: Right now, I'm unable to]

547
00:35:55,150 --> 00:35:58,150
[Taichi: say I like you with conviction.]

548
00:35:58,160 --> 00:36:00,820
[Taichi: And for you, on the receiving end,]

549
00:36:00,820 --> 00:36:02,300
[Taichi: it's hard for you to accept]

550
00:36:02,300 --> 00:36:03,810
[Taichi: that I'm sincere right away,]

551
00:36:03,810 --> 00:36:07,420
[Taichi: since we've been
a lot like buddies so far.]

552
00:36:07,420 --> 00:36:13,280
[Cho Yun Jae: To be honest,
I like that I'm relaxed around you, but...]

553
00:36:13,280 --> 00:36:16,850
[Cho Yun Jae: I don't know if it's romantic
or just because it's fun.]

554
00:36:16,860 --> 00:36:20,300
[Cho Yun Jae: To be honest, on the first day,
when I went on a date with you,]

555
00:36:20,320 --> 00:36:22,860
[Cho Yun Jae: I was grateful
that you chose me,]

556
00:36:22,880 --> 00:36:25,090
[Cho Yun Jae: so I was quite fond of you.]

557
00:36:25,090 --> 00:36:27,910
[Cho Yun Jae: But after the date,]

558
00:36:27,920 --> 00:36:32,750
[Cho Yun Jae: I felt like
you weren't interested in me anymore.]

559
00:36:32,760 --> 00:36:37,510
[Cho Yun Jae: So I saw you as a friend,
but you called me today.]

560
00:36:37,510 --> 00:36:41,790
[Cho Yun Jae: To be honest, I was happy.]

561
00:36:41,810 --> 00:36:45,380
[Cho Yun Jae: But anyway, we already]

562
00:36:45,380 --> 00:36:49,580
[Cho Yun Jae: know a lot about each other.]
[Taichi: That's right.]

563
00:36:49,580 --> 00:36:54,080
[Cho Yun Jae: Like how
I've been interested in Hyun Jun,]

564
00:36:54,090 --> 00:36:58,700
[Cho Yun Jae: and...
Since Han Gyeol and I are roommates,]

565
00:36:58,700 --> 00:37:01,070
[Cho Yun Jae: I know that
you two were a thing.]

566
00:36:58,820 --> 00:36:59,580
Yeah.

567
00:37:01,780 --> 00:37:04,140
[Cho Yun Jae: I don't know what to think.]
[Taichi: Me too.]

568
00:37:04,140 --> 00:37:06,700
[Cho Yun Jae: So I wanted to talk to you.]
[Taichi: Today...]

569
00:37:06,700 --> 00:37:09,670
[Taichi: In this brief time, I was quite
surprised by our similar sense of humor]

570
00:37:09,680 --> 00:37:12,070
[Taichi: and how fun it was
to hang out with you.]

571
00:37:12,070 --> 00:37:14,330
[Taichi: It's rare for me to feel this way.]

572
00:37:14,330 --> 00:37:15,220
[Cho Yun Jae: Yeah.]
[Taichi: I'm...]

573
00:37:15,220 --> 00:37:17,170
[Taichi: I'm more picky than you'd think.]

574
00:37:17,170 --> 00:37:19,840
[Taichi:
I don't get along with people easily.]

575
00:37:19,850 --> 00:37:21,480
[Taichi: It takes me a long time
to feel close to others.]

576
00:37:21,480 --> 00:37:22,720
[Cho Yun Jae: Me too.]

577
00:37:22,720 --> 00:37:26,020
[Taichi: But it was different for us. So...]

578
00:37:26,050 --> 00:37:28,540
[Taichi: This could be
a kind of attraction.]

579
00:37:28,560 --> 00:37:30,210
[Cho Yun Jae: Yeah.]
[Taichi: But... So...]

580
00:37:30,220 --> 00:37:33,270
[Taichi: The person
I want to talk with now is you.]

581
00:37:33,280 --> 00:37:37,390
[Taichi: I think we can have a good chat,]

582
00:37:37,400 --> 00:37:40,560
[Taichi: so I thought
it's right to choose you.]

583
00:37:40,570 --> 00:37:42,740
[Taichi: Right now, to be really honest,]

584
00:37:42,750 --> 00:37:44,500
[Taichi: since you came to me,]

585
00:37:44,500 --> 00:37:47,110
[Taichi: I must tell you I'm not sure.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Right?]

586
00:37:47,110 --> 00:37:48,360
[Taichi: I'm used to
having a crush on others.]

587
00:37:48,360 --> 00:37:49,840
[Taichi: If I like someone,]

588
00:37:49,840 --> 00:37:53,100
[Taichi: I'll keep liking the same person.]

589
00:37:53,100 --> 00:37:55,010
[Taichi: That's how it's been.]

590
00:37:55,010 --> 00:37:57,880
[Taichi: But on this shoot,
I've yet to feel]

591
00:37:57,880 --> 00:38:00,350
[Taichi: that kind of
intense attraction so far.]

592
00:38:00,370 --> 00:38:02,900
[Taichi: Anyway, right now I'm just]

593
00:38:02,910 --> 00:38:05,510
[Taichi: amazed that we got close so fast.]

594
00:38:05,510 --> 00:38:09,650
[Taichi: You seem interesting,
and fun to hang out with.]

595
00:38:09,650 --> 00:38:12,170
[Taichi: If I had someone I liked,
I wouldn't have]

596
00:38:12,200 --> 00:38:14,220
[Taichi: read into these feelings.]

597
00:38:14,220 --> 00:38:15,590
[Taichi: Because when I liked someone,]

598
00:38:15,600 --> 00:38:18,170
[Taichi: I've always only been
focused on that one person.]

599
00:38:18,170 --> 00:38:20,710
[Taichi: I can't say I'm certain right now.]

600
00:38:20,710 --> 00:38:22,700
[Taichi: I'm sorry about that.]

601
00:38:22,710 --> 00:38:24,040
[Cho Yun Jae: It's OK.]

602
00:38:24,040 --> 00:38:28,450
[Cho Yun Jae: But it's great
that you're honest with me.]

603
00:38:28,450 --> 00:38:31,180
[Taichi: I should be honest.]

604
00:38:31,200 --> 00:38:36,550
[Cho Yun Jae:
I've been honest too, ya know?]

605
00:38:36,550 --> 00:38:38,810
[Taichi: "Ya know"?]
[Cho Yun Jae: Ya know.]

606
00:38:38,830 --> 00:38:41,960
[Taichi: Me too, ya know?]

607
00:38:42,200 --> 00:38:45,990
[Will Yun Jae's feelings change?]

608
00:38:47,580 --> 00:38:51,260
[Who set your heart ablaze today?
Record it in your Love Diary.]

609
00:38:53,220 --> 00:38:56,540
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Is the thought of
writing your Love Diary getting you excited?]

610
00:38:56,860 --> 00:38:58,700
[Hahaha.]

611
00:39:11,220 --> 00:39:12,500
Oh my goodness...

612
00:39:18,100 --> 00:39:19,700
[Staring]

613
00:39:19,500 --> 00:39:20,180
What?

614
00:39:21,620 --> 00:39:23,890
[Eum Hyeok Jin: What?]

615
00:39:28,130 --> 00:39:32,500
[Sun Wook is
looking through his past entries]

616
00:39:32,570 --> 00:39:36,000
[Kim Sun Wook: Wow, from the first day,
I've only written about Hyun Jun.]

617
00:39:36,000 --> 00:39:38,540
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It's been the same for me.]

618
00:39:43,580 --> 00:39:44,980
[My heart is: Sunny
Most drawn to: Lee Hyun Jun (❤️⁠x6½)]

619
00:39:44,980 --> 00:39:49,370
[Kim Sun Wook: All I've written is Hyun Jun.]

620
00:39:44,980 --> 00:39:49,370
["I'm happy I got to talk a lot with Hyun Jun.
I got a call from him for the first time.
Feels like a dream!"]

621
00:39:49,370 --> 00:39:54,180
[Kim Sun Wook: Yeah, just about Lee Hyun Jun.]

622
00:39:55,580 --> 00:39:58,900
[Eum Hyeok Jin: My heart was partly cloudy.]

623
00:39:55,580 --> 00:39:58,900
["After I missed the chance yesterday,
I got prepared first thing in the morning.]

624
00:39:58,900 --> 00:40:02,860
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I was a bit relieved,
