625
00:39:58,900 --> 00:40:02,860
[But I couldn't go on a date again. And it
had to be Taichi, who chose Han Gyeol.]

626
00:40:02,860 --> 00:40:06,460
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I was a bit comforted,]

627
00:40:02,860 --> 00:40:06,460
[What's wrong with me? I was so sad that I
cried in front of Han Gyeol. I felt energized
by the group date, my first time out of the dorm!]

628
00:40:06,460 --> 00:40:08,170
[Eum Hyeok Jin: so I feel refreshed.]

629
00:40:06,460 --> 00:40:08,170
[Most drawn to: Kim Han Gyeol (❤️⁠x6½)]

630
00:40:08,180 --> 00:40:12,740
[Hyeok Jin's Mind = bowling was super fun
+ must have a date tomorrow + first time
getting his call; sincerity wins hearts?
+ Am I warm? + craving Melona]

631
00:40:08,180 --> 00:40:10,460
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Bowling was fun]

632
00:40:10,460 --> 00:40:12,740
[Eum Hyeok Jin: and I felt better.]

633
00:40:12,740 --> 00:40:18,520
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Han Gyeol said I'm
now his priority. Persistence paid off.]

634
00:40:18,520 --> 00:40:21,740
[Eum Hyeok Jin: My no. 1 is Han Gyeol.
No one's my least favorite.]

635
00:40:21,740 --> 00:40:26,370
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm happy today,
so everything seems beautiful.]

636
00:40:28,210 --> 00:40:34,000
[Lee Hyeong Jun: The date was fun,
but it was a busy day,]

637
00:40:28,210 --> 00:40:34,000
[Most drawn to: Min Seong (❤️⁠x4)
Least drawn to: Han Gyeol (x1)]

