00:53:29,570 --> 00:53:31,930
[Cho Yun Jae: It's transparent.]

837
00:53:31,930 --> 00:53:34,490
[Lee Hyun Jun: There's a scent. Or not?]

838
00:53:34,490 --> 00:53:36,410
[Cho Yun Jae: No, I smell it too.]

839
00:53:36,810 --> 00:53:38,490
[Lee Hyun Jun: It looks warm.]

840
00:53:38,610 --> 00:53:41,210
[Lee Hyun Jun: Do you like saunas?]
[Cho Yun Jae: Yes, I do.]

841
00:53:41,210 --> 00:53:45,050
[Cho Yun Jae:
I feel like it relieves fatigue.]

842
00:53:45,050 --> 00:53:47,850
[Lee Hyun Jun: Let's get changed.]
[Cho Yun Jae: OK.]

843
00:53:48,250 --> 00:53:51,050
[What will unfold in this special place?]

844
00:53:48,420 --> 00:53:49,480
It's fascinating.

845
00:53:53,220 --> 00:53:54,020
It's cold.

846
00:53:56,490 --> 00:53:59,510
[Cho Yun Jae: Where should we leave this?
Can we drink in the tub?]

847
00:53:59,510 --> 00:54:01,130
[Lee Hyun Jun: Yeah, they said we can.]

848
00:54:01,490 --> 00:54:05,810
[Lee Hyun Jun: I've never had a date like this.
And it was with someone I've never dated.]

849
00:54:05,810 --> 00:54:11,090
[Lee Hyun Jun:
It was a novel date, so I liked it.]

850
00:54:16,370 --> 00:54:17,170
[Lee Hyun Jun: Oh!]

851
00:54:22,450 --> 00:54:25,450
[Lee Hyun Jun: It's a bit hot.]
[Cho Yun Jae: It's really hot.]

852
00:54:26,770 --> 00:54:29,610
[Lee Hyun Jun: Are you OK?]
[Cho Yun Jae: Yeah, I'm fine.]

853
00:54:31,970 --> 00:54:34,370
[Cho Yun Jae: I'm hot.]
[Lee Hyun Jun: You're hot?]

854
00:54:34,370 --> 00:54:38,690
[Cho Yun Jae: It's hot.]
[Lee Hyun Jun: It's warm for me. Just nice.]

855
00:54:39,650 --> 00:54:41,050
[Lee Hyun Jun: When was the last time
you had a sauna?]

856
00:54:41,050 --> 00:54:43,770
[Cho Yun Jae: Sauna? It's been a long time.]

857
00:54:43,770 --> 00:54:47,130
[Cho Yun Jae: Really long. Years ago.]
[Lee Hyun Jun: That long?]

858
00:54:47,970 --> 00:54:53,810
[Lee Hyun Jun: I had a sauna sometime last year.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Where did you go?]

859
00:54:53,810 --> 00:54:54,810
[Lee Hyun Jun: In my neighborhood.]

860
00:54:54,810 --> 00:54:58,610
[Cho Yun Jae: A sauna in the neighborhood.]
[Lee Hyun Jun: In my neighborhood.]

861
00:54:58,610 --> 00:55:00,010
[Lee Hyun Jun: I've never been
to an outdoor sauna.]

862
00:55:00,010 --> 00:55:03,770
[Cho Yun Jae: Me too. It feels like Japan, right?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Yeah.]

863
00:55:04,450 --> 00:55:09,370
[Cho Yun Jae: How do you feel being out here?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: How I feel? It's fun.]

864
00:55:09,370 --> 00:55:12,570
[Cho Yun Jae: Really?]

865
00:55:13,210 --> 00:55:15,890
[Lee Hyun Jun: I need to stand up.]

866
00:55:14,860 --> 00:55:15,920
Oh, lean like this?

867
00:55:18,060 --> 00:55:19,220
Sit there.

868
00:55:24,890 --> 00:55:26,330
[Cho Yun Jae: You must work out a lot.]

869
00:55:26,330 --> 00:55:31,290
[Lee Hyun Jun: Work out?
I just do simple stuff.]

870
00:55:31,290 --> 00:55:34,970
[Lee Hyun Jun:
I used to go 5 or 6 days a week.]

871
00:55:34,970 --> 00:55:39,170
[Lee Hyun Jun: Now I'm lazy and go 4 days.]

872
00:55:39,970 --> 00:55:41,650
[Lee Hyun Jun: I've been lazy.]

873
00:55:41,650 --> 00:55:45,010
[Cho Yun Jae: The weather's too good.
I'm so hot.]

874
00:55:45,010 --> 00:55:48,250
[Lee Hyun Jun: Wipe with the towel.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Yeah, I should.]

875
00:55:51,490 --> 00:55:52,530
[Cho Yun Jae: Do you need it?]

876
00:55:58,460 --> 00:55:59,940
[Ha...]

877
00:56:00,930 --> 00:56:04,650
[Lee Hyun Jun: How do you feel
being out on a date?]

878
00:56:05,530 --> 00:56:08,570
[Cho Yun Jae: It's nice, but first of all...]

879
00:56:08,690 --> 00:56:12,650
[I'm happy because I'm with you.]

880
00:56:12,650 --> 00:56:15,930
[Lee Hyun Jun: What did you want to do?
Bungee jumping? You kept mentioning it.]

881
00:56:15,930 --> 00:56:18,850
[Cho Yun Jae: I want to do extreme sports.]

882
00:56:18,850 --> 00:56:20,570
[Lee Hyun Jun: There are
other things besides bungee jumping.]

883
00:56:20,570 --> 00:56:23,730
[Cho Yun Jae: I've tried most of the scary stuff.]
[Lee Hyun Jun: What have you tried?]

884
00:56:23,730 --> 00:56:27,650
[Cho Yun Jae: There are many scary
theme park rides in Southeast Asia.]

885
00:56:27,650 --> 00:56:29,210
[Cho Yun Jae: I've tried them all.]

886
00:56:29,210 --> 00:56:32,930
[Lee Hyun Jun:
So you've been to Gyeongju World too?]

887
00:56:32,930 --> 00:56:35,770
[Cho Yun Jae: I've been there.]

888
00:56:35,770 --> 00:56:38,050
[Cho Yun Jae: But I don't think
the rides in Korea are scary.]

889
00:56:38,050 --> 00:56:44,770
[Lee Hyun Jun: Gyeongju World rides are scary.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Rides abroad, there are]

890
00:56:45,210 --> 00:56:47,970
[Cho Yun Jae: like roller coasters
that go backwards.]

891
00:56:47,970 --> 00:56:51,650
[Lee Hyun Jun: I saw it on YouTube.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Keeps going backwards. It was fun.]

892
00:56:51,650 --> 00:56:54,450
[Cho Yun Jae: I went with a friend,
and they threw up after.]

893
00:56:54,450 --> 00:56:56,290
[Cho Yun Jae: It makes you really dizzy.]

894
00:56:56,290 --> 00:57:00,770
[Lee Hyun Jun: Did you try it too?]
[Cho Yun Jae: I did, but I was OK.]

895
00:57:00,770 --> 00:57:03,850
[Lee Hyun Jun: Really? I'm curious.
I want to try it too.]

896
00:57:03,850 --> 00:57:05,210
[Cho Yun Jae: It's getting cold.]

897
00:57:06,130 --> 00:57:07,610
[Lee Hyun Jun: Do you travel a lot?]

898
00:57:07,610 --> 00:57:09,610
[Cho Yun Jae: I like traveling.]

899
00:57:09,610 --> 00:57:12,810
[Lee Hyun Jun: Really?]
[Cho Yun Jae: I actually like active stuff.]

900
00:57:12,810 --> 00:57:14,730
[Lee Hyun Jun:
I don't think you're an introvert.]

901
00:57:14,730 --> 00:57:17,970
[Cho Yun Jae: Interpersonal relationships
and being active are different.]

902
00:57:18,450 --> 00:57:22,570
[Cho Yun Jae: I feel uncomfortable and shy
when there are many people around.]

903
00:57:22,570 --> 00:57:26,290
[Cho Yun Jae: But...
I think they're different.]

904
00:57:27,090 --> 00:57:29,690
[Lee Hyun Jun: I get too lazy to travel.]

905
00:57:29,690 --> 00:57:33,170
[Lee Hyun Jun: It's nice once you get there,
but the process is troublesome.]

906
00:57:30,860 --> 00:57:31,420
Right?

907
00:57:33,170 --> 00:57:37,850
[Cho Yun Jae: Booking tickets and hotels.]
[Lee Hyun Jun: And there's also waiting in line]

908
00:57:37,850 --> 00:57:40,530
[Lee Hyun Jun: at the airport and stuff.]

909
00:57:40,530 --> 00:57:43,690
[Cho Yun Jae: That's troublesome.]

910
00:57:43,690 --> 00:57:46,010
[Lee Hyun Jun: The line is too long.]

911
00:57:46,010 --> 00:57:49,970
[Lee Hyun Jun: At the immigration counter.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Yeah.]

912
00:57:51,130 --> 00:57:56,690
[Cho Yun Jae: Do you talk a lot with friends?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Me?]

913
00:57:56,690 --> 00:58:01,650
[Lee Hyun Jun: I'm quiet when with friends too.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Right? You seem quiet.]

914
00:58:01,650 --> 00:58:04,610
[Lee Hyun Jun: I just listen
and speak from time to time.]

915
00:58:04,610 --> 00:58:07,490
[Lee Hyun Jun: I've always been quiet.]

916
00:58:07,490 --> 00:58:10,370
[Lee Hyun Jun: No, I changed.]
[Cho Yun Jae: You did?]

917
00:58:10,370 --> 00:58:11,650
[Lee Hyun Jun: When I was little,]

918
00:58:11,650 --> 00:58:15,130
[Lee Hyun Jun:
I talked a lot in elementary school.]

919
00:58:15,130 --> 00:58:19,170
[Lee Hyun Jun: I changed after puberty.]
[Cho Yun Jae: I see.]

920
00:58:19,170 --> 00:58:22,530
[Lee Hyun Jun: They say
I suddenly became quiet.]

921
00:58:22,530 --> 00:58:24,890
[Lee Hyun Jun: I stopped talking after that.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Why?]

922
00:58:24,890 --> 00:58:26,450
[Lee Hyun Jun: It's troublesome.]

923
00:58:28,970 --> 00:58:33,450
[Lee Hyun Jun: Or should I say
I just don't like speaking unnecessarily?]

924
00:58:34,370 --> 00:58:36,540
[Cho Yun Jae: Oh.]

925
00:58:36,540 --> 00:58:39,410
[Lee Hyun Jun: I guess
I thought it was better to]

926
00:58:39,410 --> 00:58:42,010
[Lee Hyun Jun: talk only when necessary.]

927
00:58:43,050 --> 00:58:45,110
[Lee Hyun Jun: Did you say
you've never been in a relationship?]

928
00:58:45,110 --> 00:58:48,770
[Cho Yun Jae: No, just not many.]

929
00:58:48,930 --> 00:58:50,850
[Lee Hyun Jun: How many times?]

930
00:58:51,450 --> 00:58:54,650
[Cho Yun Jae: Twice after turning 20.]

931
00:58:54,650 --> 00:58:58,250
[Lee Hyun Jun: Twice? How long were they?]

932
00:58:58,610 --> 00:59:02,770
[Cho Yun Jae: One was around 6 months,]

933
00:59:02,770 --> 00:59:05,970
[Cho Yun Jae: and the other was long-term.]

934
00:59:05,970 --> 00:59:09,890
[Cho Yun Jae: I met him for a few years.]

935
00:59:09,890 --> 00:59:14,570
[Cho Yun Jae: I think it's a reason
I don't date much.]

936
00:59:14,570 --> 00:59:20,010
[Cho Yun Jae: After dating someone long-term.
What about you?]

937
00:59:20,010 --> 00:59:22,770
[Lee Hyun Jun: Twice too.]
[Cho Yun Jae: After 20?]

938
00:59:22,770 --> 00:59:26,050
[Lee Hyun Jun: Yeah, I've never
been in a relationship before 20.]

939
00:59:26,050 --> 00:59:29,370
[Cho Yun Jae: None before 20?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Yeah.]

940
00:59:29,370 --> 00:59:32,890
[Lee Hyun Jun: My first time was
after coming to Seoul.]

941
00:59:33,490 --> 00:59:36,530
[Cho Yun Jae: What kind of relationship
do you want?]

942
00:59:36,530 --> 00:59:38,930
[Lee Hyun Jun: Me?]

943
00:59:38,930 --> 00:59:42,210
[Lee Hyun Jun: Where we're like friends.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Like friends?]

944
00:59:42,210 --> 00:59:45,290
[Lee Hyun Jun: Relaxed but nice.]
[Cho Yun Jae: I see.]

945
00:59:45,290 --> 00:59:49,690
[Lee Hyun Jun: What about you?]
[Cho Yun Jae: Same for me.]

946
00:59:49,690 --> 00:59:55,010
[Cho Yun Jae: When we're together,
I'd like to feel like I'm having fun.]

947
00:59:55,010 --> 00:59:56,290
[Lee Hyun Jun: I see. Fun.]

948
00:59:56,290 --> 01:00:02,610
[Cho Yun Jae: Actually, I...
I also like the quiet vibe too.]

949
01:00:02,610 --> 01:00:04,410
[Cho Yun Jae: The silence when we don't talk.]

950
01:00:05,330 --> 01:00:07,490
[Cho Yun Jae: You get me?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Being comfortable with each other?]

951
01:00:07,490 --> 01:00:13,290
[Cho Yun Jae: Yes, when
we're comfortable even in silence.]

952
01:00:13,300 --> 01:00:15,290
[Lee Hyun Jun: I think I get it.]

953
01:00:19,570 --> 01:00:22,930
[Lee Hyun Jun: Oops, sorry.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Was that a challenge?]

954
01:00:22,930 --> 01:00:26,290
[Lee Hyun Jun: I'll win if we fight.]
[Cho Yun Jae: You're right.]

955
01:00:26,290 --> 01:00:29,730
[Cho Yun Jae: Every time you move,
this wobbles too.]

956
01:00:30,170 --> 01:00:33,850
[Lee Hyun Jun: Nah, not to that extent.]
[Cho Yun Jae: No, it is.]

957
01:00:38,250 --> 01:00:42,610
[A conversation that is
slightly smooth and slightly choppy]

958
01:00:42,610 --> 01:00:45,490
[Lee Hyun Jun: Want to go into the sauna?]
[Cho Yun Jae: Yeah, let's go in.]

959
01:00:48,890 --> 01:00:50,690
[Cho Yun Jae: How do you make this again?]

960
01:00:51,250 --> 01:00:53,210
[Lee Hyun Jun: A towel sheep head?]
[Cho Yun Jae: Yeah.]

961
01:00:53,210 --> 01:00:55,690
[Cho Yun Jae: Right, I remember now.]

962
01:00:55,690 --> 01:00:59,490
[Cho Yun Jae: But it might not look good.
Do you want to try it on?]

963
01:00:59,490 --> 01:01:01,410
[Lee Hyun Jun: No, I'm good.]

964
01:01:01,410 --> 01:01:06,250
[Cho Yun Jae: Try it. Just try it.]
[Lee Hyun Jun: No, I'm good.]

965
01:01:04,740 --> 01:01:06,340
-Try it. -I'm good.

966
01:01:07,210 --> 01:01:10,330
[Lee Hyun Jun: I don't really like sheep.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Why not?]

967
01:01:10,330 --> 01:01:14,490
[Lee Hyun Jun: Sheep?]
[Cho Yun Jae: Why? Sheep are cute.]

968
01:01:14,490 --> 01:01:18,770
[Lee Hyun Jun:
They are, but I prefer goats.]

969
01:01:19,370 --> 01:01:22,210
[Cho Yun Jae: Why do you like goats more?]

970
01:01:22,210 --> 01:01:26,210
[Lee Hyun Jun: Goats are cuter.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Really?]

971
01:01:27,730 --> 01:01:29,210
[Cho Yun Jae: This is...]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Try it on.]

972
01:01:29,210 --> 01:01:31,530
[Cho Yun Jae: You try it on.]
[Lee Hyun Jun: I don't want to.]

973
01:01:31,530 --> 01:01:33,250
[Lee Hyun Jun: Try it on.]

974
01:01:32,900 --> 01:01:33,540
Here.

975
01:01:34,820 --> 01:01:37,550
[Cho Yun Jae: Is this how you wear it?
It doesn't fit.]

976
01:01:37,550 --> 01:01:40,290
[Lee Hyun Jun:
You probably made it too tight.]

977
01:01:40,290 --> 01:01:41,770
[Lee Hyun Jun: You look like a sheep.]

978
01:01:41,770 --> 01:01:45,090
[Cho Yun Jae: Do I?
Don't you dislike sheep?]

979
01:01:45,090 --> 01:01:47,850
[Lee Hyun Jun: But you look like a sheep.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Do I?]

980
01:01:47,850 --> 01:01:50,970
[Cho Yun Jae: Didn't you say
sheep aren't cute? That you prefer goats?]

981
01:01:50,970 --> 01:01:53,170
[Lee Hyun Jun: I did.]

982
01:01:53,170 --> 01:01:55,010
[Lee Hyun Jun: With the towel on,
you look like a sheep.]

983
01:01:56,090 --> 01:01:58,050
[Lee Hyun Jun: It suits you.]

984
01:02:10,650 --> 01:02:12,890
[Cho Yun Jae: It looks nice from here.]

985
01:02:12,890 --> 01:02:14,140
[Lee Hyun Jun: The scenery?]

986
01:02:14,150 --> 01:02:17,450
[Lee Hyun Jun: I liked it from the outside too.
Since the weather's great today.]

987
01:02:18,490 --> 01:02:21,210
[Cho Yun Jae: I find it
more beautiful looking out from here.]

988
01:02:21,210 --> 01:02:23,050
[Cho Yun Jae: Like it's being framed.]

989
01:02:23,050 --> 01:02:27,490
[Lee Hyun Jun: I see,
framed by the window.]

990
01:02:29,250 --> 01:02:30,970
[Lee Hyun Jun: It feels like Finland.]

991
01:02:31,930 --> 01:02:35,530
[Cho Yun Jae: R-R-Really.]

992
01:02:35,530 --> 01:02:38,780
[Lee Hyun Jun: Though I've never been there.]

993
01:02:38,780 --> 01:02:40,700
[Lee Hyun Jun: It feels like I'm abroad.]

994
01:02:41,290 --> 01:02:43,490
[Cho Yun Jae: Do you want to go?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Finland?]

995
01:02:43,490 --> 01:02:44,890
[Cho Yun Jae: Yeah.]
[Lee Hyun Jun: No.]

996
01:02:44,890 --> 01:02:48,090
[Cho Yun Jae: Why?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: It's a long flight.]

997
01:02:48,090 --> 01:02:51,170
[Cho Yun Jae: Can't stand long-distance flights?]
[Lee Hyun Jun: Yeah.]

998
01:02:51,770 --> 01:02:53,430
[Lee Hyun Jun: Regular seats
are too narrow for me.]

999
01:02:53,430 --> 01:02:54,890
[Cho Yun Jae: Right, they should be.]

1000
01:02:54,890 --> 01:02:58,170
[Lee Hyun Jun: Even flights
to Jeju Island or Japan are tough.]

1001
01:02:58,170 --> 01:03:01,460
[Cho Yun Jae: I can't sit for too long too,]

1002
01:03:01,460 --> 01:03:05,940
[Cho Yun Jae: so I go to
the bathroom area to stretch.]

1003
01:03:05,940 --> 01:03:07,970
[Cho Yun Jae:
Stretch a little and come back.]

1004
01:03:07,400 --> 01:03:08,340
I usually do that.

1005
01:03:07,970 --> 01:03:11,890
[Lee Hyun Jun: But I can't keep doing that.]
[Cho Yun Jae: I keep doing it.]

1006
01:03:11,890 --> 01:03:13,530
[Lee Hyun Jun: That's why
I don't like going abroad.]

1007
01:03:13,530 --> 01:03:15,170
[Lee Hyun Jun: I don't like plane rides.]

1008
01:03:15,170 --> 01:03:17,310
[Lee Hyun Jun: The whole process is
inconvenient and troublesome.]

1009
01:03:17,310 --> 01:03:19,450
[Cho Yun Jae: Yeah, packing luggage too.]

1010
01:03:19,450 --> 01:03:21,770
[Cho Yun Jae:
But it's exciting too. For me.]

1011
01:03:22,330 --> 01:03:23,520
[Lee Hyun Jun: Packing luggage?]

1012
01:03:23,520 --> 01:03:26,010
[Lee Hyun Jun: I find it troublesome.]
[Cho Yun Jae: Oh, really?]

1013
01:03:30,730 --> 01:03:33,930
[Cho Yun Jae: Although we
talked more than usual,]

1014
01:03:33,930 --> 01:03:38,570
[Cho Yun Jae:
I don't think our conversation]

1015
01:03:38,570 --> 01:03:40,660
[Cho Yun Jae: flowed well.]

1016
01:03:40,660 --> 01:03:43,860
[Cho Yun Jae: The romantic excitement
I felt at the start]

1017
01:03:43,860 --> 01:03:46,850
[Cho Yun Jae: has been decreasing.]

1018
01:03:47,650 --> 01:03:50,050
[Lee Hyun Jun:
On my first date with Yun Jae,]

1019
01:03:50,730 --> 01:03:53,740
[Lee Hyun Jun:
the conversational flow wasn't bad,]

1020
01:03:53,740 --> 01:03:55,980
[Lee Hyun Jun: but I can't say]

1021
01:03:55,980 --> 01:03:59,930
[Lee Hyun Jun: it was smooth either.]

1022
01:03:59,930 --> 01:04:05,210
[Lee Hyun Jun: I strongly felt
that we'd be better as buddies]

1023
01:04:05,210 --> 01:04:08,810
[Lee Hyun Jun: than romantic partners.]

1024
01:04:09,970 --> 01:04:19,120
[Are they losing interest
in each other for good?]

1025
01:04:19,850 --> 01:04:23,620
[The sun shines brightly by the river]

1026
01:04:25,220 --> 01:04:28,120
[Eum Hyeok Jin: The weather is so nice.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yeah.]

1027
01:04:28,130 --> 01:04:30,980
[Kim Han Gyeol: I like walking, so I've
always wanted to come to places like these.]

1028
01:04:30,980 --> 01:04:35,230
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yeah, you said that
in the first meeting.]

1029
01:04:34,220 --> 01:04:34,700
Yes.

1030
01:04:36,080 --> 01:04:38,260
[Kim Han Gyeol: For the person
who I've never dated before,]

1031
01:04:38,280 --> 01:04:39,520
[Kim Han Gyeol: I chose Eum Hyeok Jin.]

1032
01:04:40,120 --> 01:04:44,320
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I chose Han Gyeol,
who I've been wanting to go on a date with.]

1033
01:04:44,320 --> 01:04:48,780
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I was really excited
to be alone with him.]

1034
01:04:49,380 --> 01:04:53,120
[Kim Han Gyeol: How do you feel on your
first date? Your first time leaving the dorm.]

1035
01:04:53,640 --> 01:04:59,670
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm excited
because it's my first date,]

1036
01:04:59,670 --> 01:05:02,960
[Eum Hyeok Jin: and also
because it's with you.]

1037
01:05:02,960 --> 01:05:05,230
[Kim Han Gyeol:
Let's lean here for a while.]

1038
01:05:06,840 --> 01:05:11,210
[Eum Hyeok Jin: To be honest,
I'd been feeling really down.]

1039
01:05:11,210 --> 01:05:14,410
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I wanted to go out with you,]

1040
01:05:14,420 --> 01:05:20,670
[Eum Hyeok Jin: but the timing was never right.
Like I wasn't granted a chance.]

1041
01:05:20,690 --> 01:05:27,830
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It felt like
I just kept missing out on everything,]

1042
01:05:28,530 --> 01:05:31,930
[Eum Hyeok Jin: so I was really stressed out.]

1043
01:05:31,930 --> 01:05:37,990
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But yesterday, you said
you wanted to go on a date with me.]

1044
01:05:38,000 --> 01:05:40,060
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So I'm grateful.]

1045
01:05:40,410 --> 01:05:43,420
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Now that
I'm out on the date, I feel good.]

1046
01:05:43,420 --> 01:05:45,570
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'm glad you're happy.]

1047
01:05:48,360 --> 01:05:50,350
[Kim Han Gyeol: Are you satisfied
coming out with me?]

1048
01:05:50,350 --> 01:05:52,160
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yes, I'm happy.]

1049
01:05:52,160 --> 01:05:54,660
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Your hands must be cold.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Thank you.]

1050
01:05:57,560 --> 01:06:03,460
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Honestly, you're the only one
I want to go on a date with.]

1051
01:06:03,460 --> 01:06:06,360
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
That's why I'm so happy today.]

1052
01:06:09,280 --> 01:06:13,730
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I kept saying
I wanted to go on a date and take a walk,]

1053
01:06:13,730 --> 01:06:16,320
[Eum Hyeok Jin: but I could never do it.]

1054
01:06:16,350 --> 01:06:21,400
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm doing everything
I wanted to do today, all at once.]

1055
01:06:21,410 --> 01:06:25,480
[Eum Hyeok Jin: So I'm really happy.]

1056
01:06:25,480 --> 01:06:28,180
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Whatever. I'm shy.]

1057
01:06:28,200 --> 01:06:31,490
[Kim Han Gyeol: That's good.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm not good at saying such stuff.]

1058
01:06:36,540 --> 01:06:42,300
[Eum Hyeok Jin: The frustration of feeling like
I was cursed has all been released instantly.]

1059
01:06:42,300 --> 01:06:43,450
[Kim Han Gyeol: That's great.]

1060
01:06:43,470 --> 01:06:47,090
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
All washed away by the river.]

1061
01:06:47,540 --> 01:06:52,020
[Kim Han Gyeol: Though we talked a lot in
Men's House, it's the first time being outside.]

1062
01:06:51,780 --> 01:06:52,220
That's right.

1063
01:06:52,020 --> 01:06:54,640
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Anyway, it's different
chatting alone in the dorm]

1064
01:06:54,640 --> 01:06:58,290
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
and chatting outside like this.]

1065
01:06:58,290 --> 01:07:00,710
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I wanted to talk to you like this.]

1066
01:07:00,730 --> 01:07:06,380
[Kim Han Gyeol:
I also think I know you better now.]

1067
01:07:06,380 --> 01:07:09,600
[Eum Hyeok Jin: How do you feel,
now that you know me better?]

1068
01:07:11,840 --> 01:07:14,240
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Gosh, I don't know!]

1069
01:07:14,240 --> 01:07:20,200
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'm very grateful to you.
You've been doing so much to woo me.]

1070
01:07:20,200 --> 01:07:23,170
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But you didn't know at first.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yeah, I didn't.]

1071
01:07:23,260 --> 01:07:25,170
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I had to tell you directly!]

1072
01:07:25,180 --> 01:07:28,190
[Eum Hyeok Jin: You know
how hard it was for me?]

1073
01:07:28,210 --> 01:07:29,720
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I was so shy.]

1074
01:07:29,720 --> 01:07:32,670
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'm a little slow.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yeah.]

1075
01:07:32,690 --> 01:07:35,120
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Want me to take your photos?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: OK.]

1076
01:07:35,120 --> 01:07:36,020
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I brought a Polaroid camera.]

1077
01:07:38,850 --> 01:07:40,770
[Kim Han Gyeol:
And I'll take photos of you.]

1078
01:07:41,120 --> 01:07:43,480
[Eum Hyeok Jin: 1, 2, 3.]

1079
01:07:45,890 --> 01:07:46,820
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It was really fun.]

1080
01:07:46,820 --> 01:07:49,130
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
I can look him in the eyes now.]

1081
01:07:49,130 --> 01:07:51,360
[Eum Hyeok Jin: His eyes are very pretty.]

1082
01:07:54,800 --> 01:07:58,080
[Kim Han Gyeol:
The date itinerary was nice.]

1083
01:07:58,640 --> 01:08:02,300
[Kim Han Gyeol: After spending time
together outside, I think we have]

1084
01:08:02,300 --> 01:08:03,460
[Kim Han Gyeol: different dating styles.]

1085
01:08:03,460 --> 01:08:06,740
[Kim Han Gyeol: On the date,
I think he was too deliberate.]

1086
01:08:06,740 --> 01:08:08,910
[Kim Han Gyeol:
That style doesn't really suit me.]

1087
01:08:08,910 --> 01:08:12,550
[Kim Han Gyeol: Especially outside.]

1088
01:08:12,780 --> 01:08:17,990
[After a walk, they move on
to the next dating activity]

1089
01:08:23,430 --> 01:08:27,770
[A tarot date to get to know each other
through tarot divination]

1090
01:08:30,600 --> 01:08:36,040
[What fate awaits them?]

1091
01:08:44,010 --> 01:08:47,950
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I'm so excited.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'm nervous.]

1092
01:08:46,939 --> 01:08:48,140
-Nervous, right? -Yes.

1093
01:08:47,950 --> 01:08:50,420
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It's my first time.]

1094
01:08:50,620 --> 01:08:52,020
[Nervous]

1095
01:08:52,220 --> 01:08:54,500
[Heart thumping]

1096
01:08:52,580 --> 01:08:54,840
First, I'll shuffle the cards properly.

1097
01:08:55,040 --> 01:08:58,350
[This is the basic card formation.
Starting from here.]

1098
01:09:00,020 --> 01:09:02,590
[It's a Queen.]

1099
01:09:03,439 --> 01:09:04,220
Kingdom.

1100
01:09:04,020 --> 01:09:08,660
[Han Gyeol got many King cards]

1101
01:09:05,020 --> 01:09:06,939
It's a King.

1102
01:09:07,080 --> 01:09:07,819
It's a bit…

1103
01:09:09,050 --> 01:09:11,029
[Eum Hyeok Jin: It's all similar.]
[Kim Han Gyeol: Yeah.]

1104
01:09:11,050 --> 01:09:12,710
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Interesting.]

1105
01:09:13,810 --> 01:09:18,850
[Kim Han Gyeol: What do you think you'll get?]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I don't know. I'm nervous.]

1106
01:09:19,040 --> 01:09:24,310
[Many of Hyeok Jin's cards
feature people and the sun]

1107
01:09:19,460 --> 01:09:20,819
I got a lot of people.

1108
01:09:20,819 --> 01:09:22,700
Seems different from mine.

1109
01:09:22,700 --> 01:09:23,899
And a lot with the sun.

1110
01:09:24,710 --> 01:09:27,880
[Hyeok Jin's cards] [Han Gyeol's cards]

1111
01:09:28,020 --> 01:09:30,590
[Hyeok Jin's cards] [Han Gyeol's cards]
[This is the basic card formation.]

1112
01:09:30,890 --> 01:09:34,850
[The cards here represent who you are.]

1113
01:09:35,380 --> 01:09:38,260
This is about love.

1114
01:09:36,500 --> 01:09:38,029
[Love Card]

1115
01:09:38,029 --> 01:09:39,270
[Fortune Card]

1116
01:09:38,260 --> 01:09:39,390
This is about money.

1117
01:09:39,450 --> 01:09:42,520
[Unlike Han Gyeol's,
I'll start with Hyeok Jin's.]

1118
01:09:42,520 --> 01:09:45,590
[There are a lot of people.
And a lot of sunshine.]

1119
01:09:43,620 --> 01:09:44,100
Yes.

1120
01:09:45,590 --> 01:09:47,300
[You have many people around you.]

1121
01:09:47,300 --> 01:09:49,800
[But his is
completely different from yours.]

1122
01:09:49,800 --> 01:09:51,569
[Rather than people,]

1123
01:09:51,569 --> 01:09:53,750
[there's a lonely queen with a long face.]

1124
01:09:53,750 --> 01:09:56,650
[You may be fine normally.]

1125
01:09:56,650 --> 01:09:59,760
[But when provoked or enraged,
you might become]

1126
01:09:59,760 --> 01:10:01,350
[quite tough.]

1127
01:10:01,370 --> 01:10:02,520
[Kim Han Gyeol:
Don't you think it's interesting?]

1128
01:10:02,520 --> 01:10:04,620
[Kim Han Gyeol: You have a lot of people,
but mine are all alone.]

1129
01:10:04,620 --> 01:10:06,320
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Yeah.]

1130
01:10:06,320 --> 01:10:10,420
[It actually ended up being
divided into two categories.]

1131
01:10:10,140 --> 01:10:11,900
-It's really fascinating. -So fascinating.

1132
01:10:10,420 --> 01:10:12,140
[Fascinating]

1133
01:10:12,620 --> 01:10:14,700
[Eum Hyeok Jin: You'd think it'd be a mix.]

1134
01:10:14,700 --> 01:10:18,310
[As for love, you got The Hierophant card.]

1135
01:10:18,310 --> 01:10:21,970
[He's preaching to the people below.]

1136
01:10:21,980 --> 01:10:26,590
[With love, you're quite tolerant.]

1137
01:10:26,590 --> 01:10:30,210
[But you could be a bit
bossy and old-fashioned.]

1138
01:10:30,220 --> 01:10:31,750
["Hey, listen to me!"]

1139
01:10:32,130 --> 01:10:33,960
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Bossy and old-fashioned?]
[Kim Han Gyeol: No.]

1140
01:10:33,960 --> 01:10:37,830
[You tend to tell your partner
to listen to you, that you're right.]

1141
01:10:37,830 --> 01:10:43,340
[But you are also very benevolent.]

1142
01:10:43,340 --> 01:10:45,130
[Kim Han Gyeol: Interesting.]

1143
01:10:45,130 --> 01:10:47,550
[You've got The Lovers card, representing
your love life in the next 3 years.]

1144
01:10:48,550 --> 01:10:53,920
[You might meet someone you get along with
and get into a relationship.]

1145
01:10:53,920 --> 01:10:56,990
[Your dating style is
completely different from his.]

1146
01:10:56,990 --> 01:10:59,390
[Unlike yours, he got a King card.]

1147
01:10:59,390 --> 01:11:00,420
[He's in a confrontation,]

1148
01:11:00,420 --> 01:11:02,770
[while you're proactively seeking love.]

1149
01:11:03,200 --> 01:11:05,850
[The person you like will appear.
You'll be surrounded by people.]

1150
01:11:06,490 --> 01:11:09,130
[With this card, there's praying.]

1151
01:11:09,620 --> 01:11:10,300
Right?

1152
01:11:10,170 --> 01:11:12,390
[And angels appear with fanfare
as you wished.]

1153
01:11:12,390 --> 01:11:14,530
[You are the one praying.]

1154
01:11:14,530 --> 01:11:19,980
[Please let me date someone like him.
You're praying like this.]

1155
01:11:20,540 --> 01:11:23,060
[Eum Hyeok Jin:
Mine was the total opposite of his.]

1156
01:11:24,780 --> 01:11:27,620
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Hmm...
I don't think the results were ideal.]

1157
01:11:28,020 --> 01:11:32,670
[Kim Han Gyeol: Just through the tarot reading,
I could see that we're totally different.]

1158
01:11:32,970 --> 01:11:36,070
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Then...]

1159
01:11:33,940 --> 01:11:34,420
Yes.

1160
01:11:36,070 --> 01:11:40,190
[Eum Hyeok Jin: If we were to date...]
[Oh, you two?]

1161
01:11:39,060 --> 01:11:40,340
Yes.

1162
01:11:40,190 --> 01:11:43,690
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I want to know
how things will turn out for us.]

1163
01:11:43,690 --> 01:11:47,190
[Will things go well if you date?]

1164
01:11:45,740 --> 01:11:46,220
Yes.

1165
01:11:46,460 --> 01:11:46,940
OK.

1166
01:11:47,200 --> 01:11:50,300
[Kim Han Gyeol: I'm curious. Since the type
of our tarot cards are totally different.]

1167
01:11:50,300 --> 01:11:52,260
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I know, right?]

1168
01:11:52,270 --> 01:11:55,690
[Brainiac, if they get into a relationship,
will it go well?]

1169
01:11:55,960 --> 01:11:58,750
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Brainiac,
please give us good cards.]

1170
01:11:59,560 --> 01:12:01,320
[Kim Han Gyeol: What will it be?]

1171
01:12:01,890 --> 01:12:05,120
[One card...
Wow, it's The Hierophant card!]

1172
01:12:06,850 --> 01:12:08,510
[This is a King card.]

1173
01:12:08,510 --> 01:12:11,480
[Rather than
getting into a relationship right away,]

1174
01:12:11,970 --> 01:12:18,060
[it's better to
coordinate your thoughts first.]

1175
01:12:18,060 --> 01:12:23,680
[For a relationship to go well,
you'll need a lot of time.]

1176
01:12:23,690 --> 01:12:27,300
[Slowly adjust to each other.]

1177
01:12:27,300 --> 01:12:32,970
[If you let nature take its course,]

1178
01:12:32,970 --> 01:12:35,370
[things can develop smoothly
between you two.]

1179
01:12:35,510 --> 01:12:39,610
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Don't be impatient.]
[Don't rush into it.]

1180
01:12:40,000 --> 01:12:43,290
[Kim Han Gyeol: What Brainiac said
sounds plausible.]

1181
01:12:44,680 --> 01:12:48,610
[Kim Han Gyeol: I thought
we weren't compatible.]

1182
01:12:48,610 --> 01:12:51,880
[Kim Han Gyeol: If we want to date,
we need a lot of time to adjust to each other.]

1183
01:12:51,890 --> 01:12:54,160
[Kim Han Gyeol: I think
that made sense to me.]

1184
01:12:54,160 --> 01:12:58,370
[Kim Han Gyeol: Personality-wise too.
Although he's older than me,]

1185
01:12:58,390 --> 01:13:04,360
[Kim Han Gyeol: I didn't get that vibe
when we were on the date.]

1186
01:13:04,370 --> 01:13:08,160
[Kim Han Gyeol: I felt a little pressured.]

1187
01:13:08,160 --> 01:13:12,380
[Eum Hyeok Jin: We asked about whether
we could be in a relationship,]

1188
01:13:12,380 --> 01:13:16,490
[Eum Hyeok Jin: and how we should
navigate things as a couple,]

1189
01:13:16,490 --> 01:13:18,580
[Eum Hyeok Jin: but the result wasn't good.]

1190
01:13:18,580 --> 01:13:20,080
[Eum Hyeok Jin: Of course,
it was just for fun.]

1191
01:13:20,080 --> 01:13:23,780
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But the reading was
that we weren't compatible,]

1192
01:13:23,780 --> 01:13:26,580
[Eum Hyeok Jin: so I was disappointed.]

1193
01:13:26,590 --> 01:13:30,450
[Eum Hyeok Jin: There's still time left
for us here. Why did we get those cards?]

1194
01:13:30,450 --> 01:13:31,900
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I can't help but]

1195
01:13:31,900 --> 01:13:36,190
[Eum Hyeok Jin: overthink things.]

1196
01:13:36,190 --> 01:13:39,960
[Eum Hyeok Jin: If our conversations
don't flow well,]

1197
01:13:39,960 --> 01:13:42,420
[Eum Hyeok Jin: or maybe
when we face some friction,]

1198
01:13:42,420 --> 01:13:48,000
[Eum Hyeok Jin: I think I'll be
reminded of this tarot reading.]

1199
01:13:48,670 --> 01:13:50,990
[How will Hyeok Jin and Han Gyeol's fate
pan out?]
